HEADWORD: Despend
<hw>De*spend"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To spend; to
squander. See <er>Dispend</er>.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Some noble men in Spain can <qex>despend</qex> ⟦pound⟧50,000.</q>
<rj><qau>Howell.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Desperado</ent>⟦br⟧
